text: I was nervous, but Dr. Celyn made me feel at ease. Highly recommend her for anyone needing help, takde hal.
Dr. Celyn is so understanding. I felt comfortable talking about my issues. The clinic is very calming, memang terbaik lah
The counseling services are very effective. The doctor is patient and highly professional. Thank you!

Dr. Celyn seems to know what she is doing but session was rushed. I was given a diagnosis but it doesn’t require medication. This costed me RM460. There are other places with better service and cheaper price than this. And I had a 3pm appointment to which I was punctual. Because their reminders mentioned any delay more than 15 mins my appointment will be cancelled and in future I won’t be able to make appointments too. But when I was punctual, they made me wait until 4pm . Only when I reminded the counter staff, the doctor called me in. Speak about punctuality, rushing the session and charging RM460. For a referral letter for any further treatment outside they charge RM80.

Dr Celyn is very professional, she makes patients feel at ease and really takes time and effort to understand their issues. She practises evidence based medicine and is a very experienced therapist.Would definitely recommend this clinic for reliable services !
